# QR Code Generator

This **QR Code Generator** is a Node.js application that allows users to generate QR codes from URLs using the **inquirer** package for input, **qr-image** for generating QR codes, and the native **fs** module for saving user input.

## Features
- **User Input**: Prompts for a URL using **inquirer**.
- **QR Code Generation**: Creates QR codes from URLs using **qr-image**.
- **File Saving**: Saves URLs to `urls.txt` with the **fs** module.
- **Downloadable Image**: Saves QR codes as PNG images.

## Installation
> Clone the repository:
   
   git clone https://github.com/abubakarcd/QR-code-generator


>Navigate to the project directory:
cd your-repo-name

>Install required packages:
npm install inquirer qr-image


>Run the application:
node index.js

Follow the prompts to enter a URL. The app generates a QR code image and saves it to your project directory, along with the URL in urls.txt.
